# Ignore everything...
*
# ...but still descend into folders to look for markdown
!*/
# ...and keep markdown files
!*.md
# ...and images, so note embeds work
!*.png
!*.jpg
!*.jpeg
!*.gif
!*.webp
!*.svg
# ...and canvases and base dashboards
!*.canvas
!*.base
# ...and Obsidian config, so the vault opens as intended
!.obsidian/**
# ...and this file itself
!.gitignore

# But never session/machine state, even inside .obsidian
.obsidian/workspace*.json
.obsidian/workspaces.json
.obsidian/webviewer.json
.obsidian/plugins/recent-files-obsidian/data*.json
# bookmarks still point at notes from the private vault
.obsidian/bookmarks.json
# proprietary font — can't be redistributed
.obsidian/apple_garamond/
# Dropbox sync artifacts
*conflicted copy*
